        <h1 class="fca-licence-car-dealers-exact-page__title">FCA Licence for Car Dealers: Do You Need FCA Authorisation?</h1>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">If your dealership offers vehicle finance to customers, you may be wondering whether you need an FCA licence.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Many car dealers become aware of FCA requirements when they start introducing customers to finance providers or assisting with vehicle finance applications. While selling vehicles alone does not usually require FCA authorisation, certain finance-related activities are regulated and may require FCA permissions.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Understanding whether your dealership requires FCA authorisation is an important part of operating compliantly and avoiding unnecessary regulatory issues.</p>
